channel.title: Worldend Devolupment
channel.description:
I am taking this project to my own level as Mahfuz may have quitten. He made the name, and the PVP for edge ville working, I made the rest. I think he has given up on it, but I will not. I am taking this, I own this 85%ish.
We share the same pics.
Dodian based. Devolution V7.
Features: Awesome Stability for Uber/WinterLove Packages. Full following Fully 100% prayer draining Facing Player Working PVP Working Bonuses help Working Defense/Str/Def system Facing NPC working prayer Str prayer works Protecting works Saving Fight Type Saving Brightness Saving Chat Full Following Don't lagg at all All mushed in a .txt file in Charactor's without those messy other files.
Videos: My economy of people and how this project pking is going just Following ATM, adding more. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l01rIzJWzVg My old Ranging system, 100% goes to KillaMess for Drawback, Delta for the Idea of NPC's getting effected by Hits. So I made Ranging Posining. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ex3qs4Gyh4k (IGNORE THE IP's, this was originally for the server feature, but it does not work anymore) So this is not called advertisement as it no longer works. Working Following & Prayer Draining http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTLbPVjtMvA
Pictures: [img]http://i386.photobucket.com/albums/oo303/k1llmachine/Fubergen0012-1.png[/img] [img]http://i386.photobucket.com/albums/oo303/k1llmachine/Fubergen0013.png[/img] [img]http://i386.photobucket.com/albums/oo303/k1llmachine/Fubergen0014.png[/img] [img]http://i386.photobucket.com/albums/oo303/k1llmachine/Fubergen0011-1.png[/img]
Credits: Bakatool 67%ish WinterLove & Daikai & Blake for the packages and stream Uber has used Mahfuz for the Base of his starting source as he made this project Me for everything added from Following - Ranging Projectile. I made everything, Mahfuz and the others that were in made up to 6 things. Not to be mean...but you didn't do much..Good job though.
